    "body": "yes - here's what happening\r\n\r\n```go\r\nvar (\r\n\tpipeFile    = \"pipe.log\"\r\n)\r\n\r\nfunc scheduleWrite() {\r\n\tfmt.Println(\"start schedule writing.\")\r\n\tf, err := os.OpenFile(pipeFile, os.O_RDWR|os.O_CREATE|os.O_APPEND, 0777)\r\n\tif err != nil {\r\n\t\tlog.Fatalf(\"error opening file: %v\", err)\r\n\t}\r\n\ti := 0\r\n\tfor {\r\n\t\tfmt.Println(\"write string to named pipe file.\")\r\n\t\tf.WriteString(fmt.Sprintf(\"test write times:%d\\n\", i))\r\n\t\ti++\r\n\t\ttime.Sleep(time.Second)\r\n\t}\r\n}\r\n\r\n```\r\n\r\nand elsewhere down\r\n\r\n```golang\r\n\t\tos.Remove(pipeFile)\r\n\t\terr := syscall.Mkfifo(pipeFile, 0666)\r\n\t\tif err != nil {\r\n\t\t\treturn err\r\n\t\t}\r\n\r\n\t\tgo scheduleWrite()\r\n\t\tfmt.Println(\"open a named pipe file for read.\")\r\n\t\tfile, err := os.OpenFile(pipeFile, os.O_CREATE, os.ModeNamedPipe)\r\n\t\tif err != nil {\r\n\t\t\treturn err\r\n\t\t}\r\n\r\n\t\treader := bufio.NewReader(file)\r\n\r\n\t\tgo func() {\r\n\t\t\tfor {\r\n\t\t\t\tline, err := reader.ReadBytes('\\n')\r\n\t\t\t\tif err == nil {\r\n\t\t\t\t\tfmt.Print(\"load string:\" + string(line))\r\n\t\t\t\t}\r\n\t\t\t}\r\n\t\t}()\r\n\r\n\t\tcl, err := rpc.Dial(pipeFile)\r\n\r\n\t\tif err != nil {\r\n\t\t\tfmt.Println(err)\r\n\t\t}\r\n\r\n\t\tconfig := console.Config{\r\n\t\t\tDataDir: *dbPath,\r\n\t\t\tDocRoot: \"\",\r\n\t\t\tClient:  cl,\r\n\t\t\tPreload: nil,\r\n\t\t}\r\n\r\n\t\tconsole, err := console.New(config)\r\n\t\tif err != nil {\r\n\t\t\tutils.Fatalf(\"Failed to start the JavaScript console: %v\", err)\r\n\t\t}\r\n\t\tdefer console.Stop(false)\r\n\r\n\t\t// Otherwise print the welcome screen and enter interactive mode\r\n\t\tconsole.Welcome()\r\n\t\tconsole.Interactive()\r\n\r\n\t}\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\nbut it explodes with \r\n\r\n```\r\nopen a named pipe file for read.\r\nstart schedule writing.\r\nwrite string to named pipe file.\r\ndial unix pipe.log: connect: connection refused\r\nload string:test write times:0\r\n\r\npanic: runtime error: invalid memory address or nil pointer dereference\r\n[signal SIGSEGV: segmentation violation code=0x1 addr=0x18 pc=0x891b8b]\r\n\r\ngoroutine 1 [running]:\r\ngithub.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/rpc.(*Client).nextID(...)\r\n\t/home/edgar/go/pkg/mod/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum@v1.10.3/rpc/client.go:237\r\ngithub.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/rpc.(*Client).newMessage(0x0, 0xeddcac, 0xb, 0x0, 0x0, 0x0, 0xf4ac08, 0xc0004e7eb0, 0x562c8b)\r\n\t/home/edgar/go/pkg/mod/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum@v1.10.3/rpc/client.go:469 +0x2b\r\ngithub.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/rpc.(*Client).CallContext(0x0, 0x1032988, 0xc003433ec0, 0xd6d060, 0xc002e811d0, 0xeddcac, 0xb, 0x0, 0x0, 0x0, ...)\r\n\t/home/edgar/go/pkg/mod/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum@v1.10.3/rpc/client.go:295 +0x108\r\ngithub.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/rpc.(*Client).SupportedModules(0x0, 0x0, 0x0, 0x0)\r\n\t/home/edgar/go/pkg/mod/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum@v1.10.3/rpc/client.go:247 +0xfe\r\ngithub.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/console.(*Console).initExtensions(0xc00013f9d0, 0xc00112b260, 0x0)\r\n\t/home/edgar/go/pkg/mod/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum@v1.10.3/console/console.go:190 +0x46\r\ngithub.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/console.(*Console).init(0xc00013f9d0, 0x0, 0x0, 0x0, 0x0, 0x30)\r\n\t/home/edgar/go/pkg/mod/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum@v1.10.3/console/console.go:121 +0x137\r\ngithub.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/console.New(0x7ffed7cbbeb4, 0x36, 0x0, 0x0, 0x0, 0xed5264, 0x2, 0x1038428, 0xc000690000, 0x1022200, ...)\r\n\t/home/edgar/go/pkg/mod/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum@v1.10.3/console/console.go:105 +0x25b\r\nmain.program(0x0, 0x0)\r\n\t/home/edgar/Repos/run-evm-code/main.go:155 +0x11ae\r\nmain.main()\r\n\t/home/edgar/Repos/run-evm-code/main.go:198 +0x8a\r\n```\r\n\r\nnot sure why it needs to immediately start querying the backend \r\n\r\nI want to have the miminial viable client -, hence i want the interface",
